<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>Surveyor</title>
		<meta charset="UTF-8">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
		<script src="default.js"></script>
		<link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="data:image/x-icon;base64,">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="default.css">
	</head>
	<body>
		<div id="Menu" class="stickytop" style="clear:both;">
			<button id="imgurUpload" onclick="createImage()">Upload Image</button>
			<button id="btnTextImport" onclick="showImport()">Text Import</button>
			<button id="btnEditItems" onclick="htmlfromjson()">Edit Fields</button>
			<button id="CustomShare" onclick="shareOptions()">Share List</button>
			<button id="EditRating" onclick="editRating()">Edit Rating</button>
			<select id="slcOptionsSwitch" onchange="SwitchOptions()">
				<option disabled selected></option>
				<option value=''>Classic</option>
				<option value=''>Detailed</option>

			</select>
			
			<span style="margin-left: 20px;">
				Background: <input id="inpSiteColour" type="color" value="#ffffff" onchange="document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--site-colour', this.value);">
				Text: <input id="inpSiteColourSecond" type="color" value="#303030" onchange="document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--site-colour-second', this.value);">
			</span>
		</div>
		<hr style="clear:both" />
		<div id="editjson" style="display:none;">
			<span id="jsonhidden" style="display:none;"></span>
			<span id="ratingshidden" style="display:none;">	
				[{"Name":0,"Description":"Hard Limit","Colour":"#000000"},{"Name":1,"Description":"Giving Only","Colour":"#ff0000"},{"Name":2,"Description":"Receiving Only","Colour":"#ffa500"},{"Name":3,"Description":"Both","Colour":"#ffff00"},{"Name":4,"Description":"Curious","Colour":"#008000"},{"Name":5,"Description":"RP Only","Colour":"#0000ff"}]
			</span>
			<span id="maxGroupNumber" style="display:none;"></span>
			<ol id="jsonbuilder" style="clear:both">
			</ol>
			<div class="stickybottom">
				<button onclick="htmltojson()">Save</button>
				<button onclick="newgroup()">Add Group</button>
				<button onclick="htmltojson('Cancel')">Cancel</button>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="divDisplay" style="clear:both;">
		</div>
		<div id="divRatingEditContainer">
			<div id="divRatingEdit"></div>
			<div class="stickybottom">
				<button id="SaveRating" onclick="saveRatingsNames()">Save Rating</button>
				<button onclick="saveRatingsNames('Cancel')">Cancel</button>			
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="divImport" style="display:none;">
			<textarea id="import" style="width:100%; height:50vh;"></textarea>
			<div>
				* Import will over-ride any current groups and items, to cancel clear the text box and press import<br>
				** Group description not currently available on import<br>
				*** Characters # ( )  * ? cannot be used other than to specify categories and , cannot be used in choice list other than to seperate choices<br>
				**** Format of text as follows:<br>
				#Group<br>
				(Choice1,Choice2)<br>
				*Item1<br>
				?Item1 Description<br>
				*Item2<br>
				?Item2 Description<br>
			</div>
			<div class="stickybottom">
				<button onclick="importitems()">Import</button>
				<button onclick="importitems('Cancel')">Cancel</button>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div id="ratingIndex">
		</div>
				
		<div id="myModal" class="modal">			
			<div class="modal-content">
				<span class="close" onclick="ChangeDisplayType('myModal', 'none')">&times;</span>
				<p id="pModalMessage">Loading...</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
